{
  "refrain": {
    "lines": [
      {
        "number": 1,
        "text": "It took a miracle to put the stars in place;"
      },
      {
        "number": 2,
        "text": "It took a miracle to hang the world in space."
      },
      {
        "number": 3,
        "text": "But when He saved my soul,"
      },
      {
        "number": 4,
        "text": "Cleansed and made me whole,"
      },
      {
        "number": 5,
        "text": "It took a miracle of love and grace!"
      }
    ]
  },
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "My Father is omnipotent"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "And that you can’t deny;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "A God of might and miracles;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "‘Tis written in the sky."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Though here His glory has been shown,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "We still can’t fully see"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "The wonders of His might, His throne;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "‘Till eternity."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "The Bible tells us of His power"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "And wisdom all way through;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And every little bird and flower"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Are testimonies, too."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    }
  ],
  "title": "It Took a Miracle"
}
